```tactics
theorem rev_eq_revAcc (l : List α) : rev l = revAcc [] l := by
  induction l with
  | nil => simp [rev, revAcc]
  | cons x xs ih =>
    simp [rev, revAcc, ih]
    all_goals try { tauto }
```

